query:
INSERT INTO entries (
                    update_number,
                    recorded_at,

                    kind,
                    parent_dir,
                    path,
                    source_id,
                    record_trigger,

                    original_size,
                    encrypted_size,
                    modified_at,
                    content_hash,
                    unix_mode,
                    is_symlink
                ) VALUES (
                    nextval('entry_update_numbers'),
                    now(),
                    $1, $2, $3, $4, $5,
                    NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, false
                ) RETURNING id
